storyInfo: An intense showdown is about to take place in Rhodes Island's training rooms. Who's going to land the title of knucklebones champion?!

attributes.content: Oh, good! Zima, Leto, over here!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Quick! No lollygagging!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: What, you need me to beat someone up?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: A fight? I'm in, I'm in!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: No, listen to me—
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I don't know what dimwit decided to flash the snacks in front of Dobermann, but I've got that, plus a bunch of the Infected kids in for introductory fitness extracurriculars! You take care of them for me, pretty please—
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Ooh, Snack Network stuff!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: You want me... to take care of kids?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I wrote everything down for you here—!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Pretty pretty please—I'll promise I'll make it up to you with a nice meal—!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Wow, Instructor Dur-nar runs fast. Is she a Kuranta?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Why ask us to look after some kids?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Wait... yeah, why us? Do we look like babysitters?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: And it's teaching a bunch of little ones who just got to Rhodes? Uhh...
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Agh. Pain in my ass.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Pssh... it's just for a day. We'll grit our teeth and bear it. Let's go.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Haha... yeah, uh...
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: All praise to the indomitable General Zima, the only woman for the job...
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Huh? Where are you going?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I'll leave you some honey! Not like I'm teaching a bunch of kids, they're all yours now! Yeah? Cool, we're cool? You've got this—
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Hey!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Kakovo khuya!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Just the thought of teaching a class gives me a headache.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Oh... sounds pretty chill?)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Okay, lucky me.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hey, hey, hey, look over here, I'm giving the orders!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: You thought you could act the big boy here? I beat you in one hit! But you're alright, you're goon #1 from today! And you're #2, and you're #3!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: This is my turf now!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Hey, new girl! You came in last, so you're the last of the goons!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: I'm the boss now, you hear? That's what you're calling me!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: (Uh-huh? She beat all these kids into submission. She's pretty solid.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Wait, no, I've gotta turn that part of my brain off. This is my class to manage.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Who died and made this scrawny brat king, huh?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Maybe she'll behave if I beat her up?)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Ugh, I can't do that. I'm an educator now.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hey, listen up, little punks! Your instructor's kind of tied up, so I'm filling in for today. Shape up!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Memo... here we go. Hey, you, with the mouth, get down from the bunker! I don't wanna hear you crying when you fall off, I'm no medic.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You don't talk to your boss like that, you goon! Cry, my butt! As if I'd ever fall off!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Yeah! Yeah!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: (Argh. Hold it in. Don't hit her. Don't hit her.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: 'Make sure they stay safe while you teach them the names of the machines and how to use them. You can also let them try training with them. But it's all about safety first!'
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Seriously, Dur-nar writes like her pen's trying to get away.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hey, get over here. Instructor Dur-nar left you some homework... Why are you standing around up there?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Pain in the... Listen to me, okay? Get down!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: No! I'm the only one allowed up here, because I'm the boss!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Yeah, yeah!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: (I'm this close to going up there and slamming her face onto the deck!)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: The instructor asked me to help watch you guys. You can't be up there, it's dangerous! Get down, now!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hmph, who cares?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: I said, get down!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You're my goon, I don't listen to you! I'm your boss! You should be listening to me!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: She's the boss! Do what she says!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Huh? You think I'm gonna do what you say? Do I seriously have to beat you up?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You can't beat me~ I'll use my Arts on you! I don't see any rocks on you, so you can't use Arts~
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: (Argh, this kid! How am I supposed to fight the urge to slug her?! Ugh, I oughta drag Leto back here and make her suffer—)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: And I'm really strong! I don't need you to look after me! I want the Instructor!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Yeah, and your instructor told me to watch you!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You're my goon, I don't need you!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: (The harder I push her, the more obnoxious she gets?)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Wish Rosa was here. I can't do goody-two-shoes model student like she can. If that girl doesn't behave, the rest of these brats won't either...)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (This is never gonna end... I need to get her under control.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You're strong, huh? I don't think so. If your instructor called me in, then I'm stronger than you, and that makes me the boss.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Don't try to lie to us! I'm the boss!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Not if I don't listen to you. What do you say we have a little contest?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Contest! Contest!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: If you lose, you have to do whatever I say. If you win, I'll be your goon!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You're my goon anyway. I don't need to do any contests.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Oh, right, I'm already your goon, I... huh?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Did I just get duped? Ugh! This sucks!)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: If you don't accept my challenge, you're a coward, the lowest goon ever. You're just scared you'll lose. You're not fit to be the boss!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: I'm the boss, you're just a goon! Let's do it, we'll have a contest!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: What are you good at?!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Knucklebones! I'm the super-duper-best at knucklebones!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: I'll show you who's the boss!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Yeah, sure, we're on.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Fight! Fight!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: I'm gonna show you what a real boss looks like, you're just a wannabe!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (I've played knucklebones a billion times. This punk's never gonna beat me...)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Alright, my turn!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Grab, toss, catch... flip, then catch, then toss, one, two, three, one...)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Done.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hmph! Anyone can do the first round.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Alright, second round then~
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Toss, catch two, toss, grab one catch one, toss, then catch...)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Drop, drop, drop!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: (Like I would! Is this girl for real...? Oh?)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (One, two, three, one... cool, cool, round 2 done.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Okay, round 3. Toss, grab, two, three, one...
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Drop! Drop! C'mon, drop!!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Read 'em and weep~ Check it out, I'm going for the last round now.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hmph, anyone could do that~ Like me!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: (Phew—okay, stay cool.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Alright, go! Grab seven, toss! Catch, toss four, then grab, then toss, catch, three, two, one, done!)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Here goes the last move, kid~
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Eight, flip, catch!)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You dropped two you dropped two!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Two drops! Two drops!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Oh, man, lost it there. Pretty decent showing, though.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Your turn. C'mon, punk, show me how you knucklebone.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hmph, I know, I know. Watch me.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: And don't call me punk. You have to call me boss.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Sure, Boss. Show me!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Ooooh, she's got skills... pretty slick movement, no wonder she's so sure of herself... definitely pretty up there. Almost done, here goes...)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Oh! You dropped three! You lose!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Alright, get over here and listen up. Also, don't ever climb on the bunker again.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Y—You cheated! That one didn't count!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: What are you talking about? You're the one trying to cheat here! Sore loser!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I'm not a sore loser! I'm not!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: I'm the boss, I can't be a sore loser!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: She's not! She's not!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Hahahahaha! We can go again if you want!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: One two three four five six seven... You grabbed seven. Progress, huh? But I got eight, so you lose again.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Alright, now it's time to shape up.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: ...Hmph.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (What? I busted my ass coming up with this and she's not even gonna keep up her end of the deal?)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Are all kids like this now?)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: If you don't make good on your word, then your, uh... goons #1 and #2 won't respect you as a boss, right?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Fine. What do you want me to do?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Learn the names of the machines and how to use them, and if you want, you can try them out a bit.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Alright, fine. Let's go.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: You got it, Boss!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: (She looks beat. Is she depressed now? Yeah, okay, kids really are a pain in the ass!)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You, uh, you're actually pretty good at knucklebones. I've just been at it longer than you, that's all. I got more practice.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Shake your wrist on the last toss, and the stones turn out like this—makes a little forward-backward separation. Scatters less if you use the back of your hand to catch, lets you catch even more.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Give it a shot.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight...
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Huh, it does.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Real handy, right? All cheered up now? Let's get going, then.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Learning time! Be good until Instructor Dur-nar gets back, and then I'll teach you the ultimate trick to knucklebones. You learn that, and you can beat anyone, anywhere.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Don't see why I'd lie to you.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Alright! You're the best, Miss!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: She's the best! She's the best!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: I'm not even teaching you, the hell are you chanting for? Listen up, class is in session!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Hah. Now I'm getting some respect.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Alright, here we go. Pay attention. This is a barbell, this rack over here's called a 'Smith machine.' You fix the barbell inside these rails here. Why do you think we do that?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: So you can't take the barbell away?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Huh? No, the Smith machine restricts how the barbell slides, so it won't swing forwards or backwards while you train. That keeps your waist or knees from getting hurt.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: This way, you can do squats... just hold it like this, then make sure your knees don't go over your feet, breathe out and crouch, breathe in and lift.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You can lie down here too, do presses, and buff up your arm strength. But you gotta watch out when you're training. Make your barbell too heavy and you can't lift it, and then if it crushes you, you're, uh. (Crosses throat and croaks)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: So be careful as you can. Got it?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Got it! If we make the barbell too heavy, it's gonna snap us in half!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Huh? Uh...
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I mean, yeah, it will if it's too heavy, so, real dangerous. Gotta watch out for that when you train.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Then this thing's a pull-up machine, horizontal and parallel bars. Back to the brace, both hands firm on the handles, then rest your arms on the beams, lift your body into the air, and do crunches like this. Works out your abs.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Uh... pretty hard to get injured on this. Anyone wanna try?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Yeah, I wanna try!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Little high for you. Lemme lift you up.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hup!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I hold on here?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Yep, then elbows up, support your own body... You got it?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Yep!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Keep your upper body fixed, back and waist straight, put pressure into your abs. Okay, legs straight, then lift them up with just your abdominal strength, breathe in, out... good.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (Shaking heavily)
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Oh, damn. You have Originium growing on your arms here. Don't chip it... does it hurt here?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Don't touch me!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Don't panic on the rack!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: What are you gonna do if you hurt yourself?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You don't grow stones, right, Miss?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: No... I don't. What's up?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Then you've gotta keep away from me.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: C'mon, get down off the rack first.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Why do I have to keep away from you?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Because I'm sick, and people keep avoiding me, and hitting me with rocks. You're not growing stones, so why aren't you keeping away?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Forget that. There's a million people growing stones here, didn't Instructor Dur-nar tell you? Focus on your training!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: When they hit you with rocks, did you fight back?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I did! Really hard!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Attagirl!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Uh... but fighting's bad, still, so don't get into dumb fights anymore.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Why?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Um... it's just bad. Listen, okay? No more random fighting from now on.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Okay.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Alright, that's enough training on this machine. Instructor Dur-nar's gonna teach you the standard stuff to do some other time, so lemme show you around the rest of the machines.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Miss, what's your name?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Huh? It's... Zima. My codename's, uh, Zima.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Codename?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Yeah, I'm called Zima now.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: How about you?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I don't have a codename yet...
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: I'll tell you once I think of one!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Haha, sure.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Cool! Lessons over. You remember all that?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Obviously! I'm really smart!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: We remember! We remember!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: You can keep doing this course with Instructor Dur-nar, if you want. Not bad to learn how to train a little.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: There's more than Instructor Dur-nar too. Other ops do some intro extracurriculars. You can go check them out, if you're into it.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Also, Rhodes Island has a bunch of other kids around your age. Go play with them, it's no sweat.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: We're done. Just waiting for Instructor Dur-nar to come back now. Let me teach you that ultimate trick for knucklebones!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: The ultimate trick!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Me too! Me too!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Sure, get over here, all of you. Watch this. But you gotta pay attention...
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Heeey, I'm back! Got it all taken care of! No skin off my back!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Hi, Instructor.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hi, Instructor.
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Oh, Zima, thanks for your help. I'll take you out to dinner in a minute~... uh, where's Leto?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Hah. She bolted as soon as she heard anything about kids.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hahaha, no dinner for her tonight then~ Talk to me, how did the classes go?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I taught them the names of all the machines and how to use them. They gave training a decent shot too. Great work all around.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Solid. I can take it from here, so you go unwind.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Sure, I'll put the machines away and stuff.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Kids, gather 'round. Let me check what you've learned, and then class is out for the day.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Umm... This is a barbell, you put it on this rack, and you fix it, so you can train your leg muscles. If you lie down here and do presses, you train your arms.
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: This is...
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: That one's...
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Nice, you've learned a lot. Does anywhere hurt after training?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Nope!
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Come here, let me just make sure now.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Mm-hm, no injuries. Good work~
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: That's it for today, then. Everyone, back to your dorms, get some proper rest. You can head to the cafeteria tonight for some of your favorites. Take a walk around, too.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Alrighty~, dismissed!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Bye, Instructor, bye, Miss Zima~
attributes.name: Infected Children

attributes.content: Bye~
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Yeah, see you.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Is Miss Zima gonna leave now?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Yep~ Today was a little special. Zima's done her duty. I'll be the one teaching you from now on.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: But... can Miss Zima come take the course with me?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Oh?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: This kiddo's gotten surprisingly attached to you, hasn't she?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Sure... huh?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You're not coming back again, Miss Zima?
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Uh. Yeah, I was just kinda helping out here today, this stuff's all too basic for me. So I guess I... um... I won't be back.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You listen to what your instructors tell you, get used to life at Rhodes. You'll have a good time.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Oh...
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Haha, isn't that funny? I never expected this.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Kiddo, what did she do that got you liking her so much?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Miss Zima told me not to get into fights anymore, fighting is bad!
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Mm-hm... oh-hoh... Zima says no fighting... pfff, okay, off you go, back to your dorm to rest~
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Okay... bye, Instructor, bye, Miss Zima...
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Miss Zima... I have class in this training room the day after tomorrow too.
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Mmwuh?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Oh, there she goes.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If I had to guess, you have no idea what she was getting at?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: She means she wants you to come see her, silly, hahaha! Just what did you do to make her fall in love with you like that?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Why don't I get that kind of treatment...? Am I too scary or something?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Ehhh? Someone's calling me... I'd better get going.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Here's my meal card. Go get yourself dinner. Just slip it under my door on your way back.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Treat yourself!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Sure. Thanks, Instructor! See you later!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Haha! Found you! I've been looking all over!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: I got us a very special honey drink!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Gah! You've got some nerve, you know that?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Ah, knock it off! I've had this in my collection forever! Za nashu druzhba~
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Hmph! You ran and left me with a pack of kids all day!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hahahahahaha, that's our General Zima, friend to children everywhere~ Hahaha!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Yeah, if only I was as good as you at retreating, General Leto!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Okay, okay, no bickering in front of the honey... drink up, come on! If this isn't an apology, I don't know what is.
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Good, right? I told you it was from my private reserve!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Mm... it's pretty good.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Come on! Tell me what babysitting capers you got up to today.
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: What are you expecting? I just ran their class.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: But... the weird thing is, there was this little girl who kind of took to me, I think...
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: A little girl who approves of you? I don't suppose you beat up her friends and scared her into submission, did you?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Do YOU want a beating?!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hey hey hey, no no, keep going keep going, I'm listening.
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Thing is... she didn't want me to leave when class was over. Said she wanted me to go to the next one with her... I'm sure as hell not going, I already know all that stuff, but...
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: What's wrong? Swallow your tongue?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: I can't figure out why.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Why what?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: She actually seems to like me...? Why?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I thought I was real strict, plus I embarrassed her by beating her in a game. Dunno about hate, but I didn't think she'd like me all that much... but then she wanted me to go to class with her?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: And I feel like I was sort of like, all, uh... you know. But she doesn't really seem to care, she just wants me to go again...
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Glug, glug, glug... phaaah! Wanna know what I think? I think you're reading too much into it, and she thinks you're great and that's why she likes you, duh!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: And besides, why would she not?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: And that's why she likes you!!!!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: We're in the cafeteria, keep it down!
attributes.name: Zima
